filament_start_gcode:
; Filament gcode
;M412 D10  ;10mm distance
;M412 S1   ; Enable runout
;M900 K0.09 ; Linear advance spring constant - tested rigid head

{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*HOTEND_AFTERBURNER_E3D.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.4} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.040{endif}  ; set E3DD Titanium
;{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_MODEL_MK2.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.4} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.07{endif}  ; set cybermk2 advance guess
;{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_MODEL_E3DD.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.4} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.07{endif}  ; set E3DD advance GUESS
